            <title>[DATAMONGO-828] UpdateFirst throws OptimisticLockingFailureException when updating document that does not exist</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/DATAMONGO-828</link>
                <project id="10701" key="DATAMONGO">Spring Data MongoDB</project>
